2888.Name: D1/D2 Women's Tournament
2888.Details:
CINCINNATI D1/D2 WOMEN’S PADDLE TOURNAMENT

Friday, January 31st

Chairs:  Amy Lutz, Suzanne Kite, & Gerry Schulze
Fee:  $60 per paddle/$120 team
*If a player is not a member of the GCPTA, there is an additional $10 per paddle

Includes: Balls, use of courts, tourney favors, lunch and finals party at HPCC.  

We are looking forward to a great tourney and are happy to help in any way. Should you have any questions, please contact
Amy Lutz @ 513.767.8000 or thelutzfamily@hotmail.com

2889.Name: GCPTA 2020 Men's City Flight #3 (Forney) D3-D6
2889.Details:
Date: Saturday  Feb 8, 2020
Time: 8am – 2pm 
Eligibility: D3-D6 GCPTA member
Cost:  $90 per team
Location:  Glendale Lyceum is the host club.  We will use clubs throughout Cincinnati for the tournament.  

Tournament will consist of a minimum of 3 matches, lunch, drinks and player favor.  

If you have any questions, please email 4knee2020@gmail.com and we will get back to you promptly.  We hope you are able to join us for another unbelievable event!

Tournament committee:  Thad Karbowsky, Jim Getgey, Jay Gohman.  They are the real Tournament Directors, Chris is just the guy that helped navigate the website!

32 Teams, $100 per team
3 matches guaranteed

Registration closes on February 28th
